'''Cornelius Nyungura''' (yavutse ku ya 24 Werurwe 1977)<ref>http://www.corneille.ca/</ref>  ni umuririmbyi uzwi kw' izina rya '''Corneille''' . Yavukiye mu Budage bw'Iburengerazuba ku babyeyi  [[Rwanda|b' abanyawanda]], yamaze igihe kinini cy'ubwana bwe mu Rwanda, amaherezo yimukira i Québec, muri Kanada mu 1997<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20150924015134/http://www.france-amerique.com/articles/2008/12/19/print/corneille-je-ne-me-sens-plus-seul-au-monde.html</ref>.  Aririmba mu Gifaransa n'Icyongereza. mu mwuga  we akunze gufatira ikitejyererezo kuri  [[:en:Funk|Funk]] y abanyamerica na soul music ; [[:en:Prince_(musician)|Prince]], [[:en:Marvin_Gaye|Marvin Gaye]] na [[:en:Stevie_Wonder|Stevie Wonder]] nibo bahanzi ajyenderaho.

== Amateka y' ubuzima bwe ==

=== Ubuzima bwe mu bwana ===
Corneille yavukiye i Freiburg im Breisgau, mu [[Ubudage|Budage]], nubwo mu bwana bwe bwose yabumaze mu Rwanda. Yavumbuye urukundo rwe muri muzika mu 1993, nuko yinjira mu itsinda rya R&amp;amp;B, ryatsinze amarushanwa ya Découverte 1993.<ref>Djenaidi, Oumelkheir. "Corneille à la conquête du marché américain". ''france-amerique.com''. France-Amerique. Archived from the original on 24 September 2015. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref>  Ibi kandi byatumye atangira kwandika indirimbo no guhimba amanota y' umuziki . cyakora, ubuzima bwe bwarahindutse nyuma ya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yakorewe abatutsi]]  mu 1994. Se, Émile Nyungura, yari umuyobozi w’ishyaka rya politiki PSD yafatwaga nk' urwanya leta bityo akaba nawe  yari mubari bwicwe; Corneille yiboneye iyicwa ry'ababyeyi be na barumuna be na bashiki be batatu afite imyaka 17.<ref>"Corneille a très envie de renouer avec le Rwanda". ''franceinfo.fr''. Radio France. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref>  yahungiye mu Budage, aho bamwe mu ncuti z' ababyeyi be bamwakiriye mu rugo rwabo. 

=== Ubuzima bwe bw' umuga ===
Muri Nyakanga 1997, Corneille yahisemo kuva mu [[Ubudage|Budage]] kugira ngo akomeze amasomo mu itumanaho, maze yimukira i [[:en:Montreal|Montreal]], muri [[:en:Quebec|Québec]], muri [[Kanada]] kugira ngo yige muri kaminuza ya Concordia . Muri icyo gihe, yashinze '''O.N.E''', itsinda rya  R&B, ari kumwe na Pierre Gage na Gardy Martin, bahuye nyuma gato yo kugera i Québec.<ref>Djenaidi, Oumelkheir. "Corneille à la conquête du marché américain". ''france-amerique.com''. France-Amerique. Archived from the original on 24 September 2015. Retrieved 13 August 2015</ref>  ''Zoukin'', imwe mu ndirimbo z'itsinda yanditswe na Corneille, yabaye iyambere muri airplay za Kanada. Hanyuma, mu ntangiriro za 2001, Corneille yavuye muri iryo tsinda, yashakaga gukomeza umwuga wenyine. Yatangiye gushingira indirimbo ze ku hahise he.<ref>Djenaidi, Oumelkheir. "Corneille à la conquête du marché américain". ''france-amerique.com''. France-Amerique. Archived from the original on 24 September 2015. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref> 

Mu 2002, Corneille yakoze imishinga itandukanye. Yanditse kandi ahimba indirimbo "Ce soir" ya ''Cocktail R&B 2'' compilation (Ghetto R&B, [[:en:Sony_Music|Sony Music]] ) na "Si seulement on s'aimait" ya ''Hip Hop Folies'' (Sony Music). Abisabwe na [[:en:Dave_Stewart_(musician_and_producer)|Dave Stewart]], yigaragaje bwa mbere kurubyiniro kuri reservoir in Paris,aho yajyiriye amahirwe yo kuririmbana  na Jimmy Cliff . Muri Mutarama 2003, yatumiriwe kuzaba ari uririmba nk ijyikorwa cyo gutegurira urubyiniro  Cunnie Williams muri Olympia .<ref>"Corneille". ''rfimusique.com''. Radio France Internationale. Retrieved 13 August 2015</ref> 

Album ya mbere ya Corneille, verisiyo yo muri Kanada ya ''Parce qu'on vient de loin'', yasohotse ku ya 10 Nzeri 2002. verisiyo  y’igifaransa, yarimo ibihembo byinshi kuri disiki ya kabiri, yasohotse ku ya 20 Ukwakira 2003, byihuse yahise imenyekana.  Muri Mata 2003,<ref>"Corneille". ''rfimusique.com''. Radio France Internationale. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref> Corneille yaririmbanye na [[:en:Craig_David|Craig David]], asubiramo umurongo mu gifaransa w' indirimbo ''Rise and Fall'' . Yakoze urugendo rwe rwa mbere muri Gicurasi 2003, aririmbira  full houses  i [[Paris]], [[:en:Marseille|Marseilles]], [[:en:Lyon|Lyon]] na [[:en:Bordeaux|Bordeaux]] . Muri Werurwe 2005, yitabiriye  igitaramo ''Africa Live,'' cyateguwe mu rwego rwo kurwanya malariya.<ref>"Corneille". ''rfimusique.com''. Radio France Internationale. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref>  Bwari ubwa mbere agaruka ku mugabane w'iwabo kuva jenoside yakorewe abatutsi yahagarikwa. Album ya kabiri ya Corneille  ''Les marchands de rêves'', yasohotse mu Gushyingo 2005. 

Corneille yakoranye na Croix-Rouge yo muri Kanada mu rwego rwo gutabariza abana bahuye n' ibibazo by' intambara.  Yasohoye alubumu ye ya mbere yo mu Cyongereza, yitwa ''Ivuka rya Koruneliyo (The birth of cornelius)'', muri Nyakanga 2007.  Mu mpera za 2014 yabaye umwe mu ba hatanaga kuri televiziyo yo mu bufaransa TF1 mw irushanwa  '''Danse avec les Stars'' . ku nshuro yaryo ya gatanu.<ref>"Corneille". ''rfimusique.com''. Radio France Internationale. Retrieved 13 August 2015</ref>

=== Eurovision ===
Corneille yanditse indirimbo " Il était temps " ayandikiye [[:en:Virginie_Pouchain|Virginie Pouchain]] nyuma yo kwemererwa guhagararira [[Ubufaransa]] mu marushanwa  ya [[:en:Eurovision_Song_Contest|Eurovision]] song contest 2006 . Indirimbo yarangije iri kumwanya wa 22 muri 24 zizari zajyeze kurwego rwa nyuma.<ref>"Eurofans 2012 : Virginie Pouchain au meeting de printemps". ''eurovision-fr.net''. Eurovision-fr.net. Retrieved 13 August 2015</ref> 

=== Ubuzima bwite ===
Corneille yashakanye n'umunyamideli ukomoka muri Kanada akaba n'umukinnyi wa filime Sofia de Medeiros mu 2006; bafite abana babiri.<ref>"Corneille et sa femme Sofia de Medeiros attendent leur premier enfant ! Cette fois, c'est officiel !". ''purepeople.com''. Pure People/Webedia. Retrieved 13 August 2015.</ref> 

